---
import ChapterLayout from "../layouts/ChapterLayout.astro";
import BookCard from "../components/BookCard.astro";
import Divider from "../components/Divider.astro";
---

<ChapterLayout title="Novels" chapter="Chapter II">
  <p class="drop-cap text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-10">
    I enjoy writing fantasy novels. First book launch coming soon!
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-8">
    <BookCard title="The Broken Ritual" amazonUrl="#">
      <p class="mb-3">An anxious graduate student, juggling the responsibilities of lectures and his floundering research.</p>
      <p class="mb-3">A slave desperately trying to discover the secrets of the fire ritual so that he might earn his freedom and see his parents once again.</p>
      <p class="mb-3">None of them were prepared for the day the water ritual stopped working. Then again, who could be prepared for something that had never happened before?</p>
      <p class="mb-3">When the water ritual breaks, the whole world must converge upon Lake Vival to reach the single source of naturally occurring drinkable water before their stores run out.</p>
      <p>The whole world, save for a small group of researchers. Instead of heading for safety, they set out on a quest for the mythical water relic, determined to bring myth into reality and restore the ritual before anyone has to die.</p>
    </BookCard>

    <Divider />



  <p class="text-center text-charcoal/50 font-heading italic text-sm mt-4">
    Maybe I'll put out more in the future. Let me know if you have any thoughts / theories on this one.
  </p>
</ChapterLayout>
